history.content:
Hi everyone!

Welcome back. We hope you all are well and looking forward to returning for Spring 22. We look forward to a new semester, meeting you all and being able to help and guide you through this journey ahead. Below are a list of our services, we are starting out remote until further notice. Remember as noted, questions can be sent to cs-advising@cs.berkeley.edu Peer advising will resume next week
history.subject: EECS Advising Services Spring 22
